&lt;p&gt;Don&amp;rsquo;t miss the &lt;a href="https://github.com/orgs/owaspsamm/discussions/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Discussions&lt;svg class="external-link-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"&gt;&lt;path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/&gt;&lt;polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/&gt;&lt;line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
 section for ideas, questions, and feedback.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>